Package: ShinyTest
Title: Proteomics of Wild-Type and Mutant KRAS Human Colorectal Cancer Samples
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Jacob",
           family = "Epstein",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "yashacode@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: An interactive Shiny application for exploring differential
    protein expression between KRAS-mutant and wild-type human colorectal
    cancer samples. Provides an interactive volcano plot, a group-averaged
    expression heatmap, and per-protein detail views with external database
    links, built on a public proteomics dataset (PRIDE PXD073413).
